{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
Love faded away with the dawning
And [G7]left me here all [C]a lone
Left me to pine for [G]my darling
My [D7]darling that once was [G]my own
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
Moon sailing on high
Please shine down with [D7]your light
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
Moon shining on high
Where is my darling [G]tonight
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 6}
Go send her my love
